  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5ef4500f111497443b1f23f4c3951502, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - Bon matin.
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f9c90a9bda4319e4680fbf0e1f897ea1, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Ce matin, quand j\u2019\xE9tais dans la calle, j\u2019ai aper\xE7u des rats. "
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1cbcf6c9bf6578c42852a9cd423df8b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Un signe d\u2019une mauvaise hygi\xE8ne si vous voulez mon avis."
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f9c90a9bda4319e4680fbf0e1f897ea1, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Mais bon, il faut s\u2019occuper de r\xE9gler \xE7a avant que \xE7a cause
      des probl\xE8mes."
